---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Base
    title="Company — KYDE"
    description="KYDE is building the trust infrastructure for the agentic economy. The governance layer that gives AI agents real economic authority while keeping humans in control."
>
    <Navbar />

    <main>
        <!-- ══════════ HERO ══════════ -->
        <section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-36 pb-24 md:pt-48 md:pb-36">
            <div class="bg-grid absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
                <p
                    class="mb-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500"
                >
                    Company
                </p>
                <div class="mb-8 h-px bg-zinc-800"></div>
                <h1
                    class="hero-h1 max-w-3xl text-5xl text-white md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl"
                >
                    The Economy Is Going Agentic.<br />
                    The Infrastructure for Trust Doesn't Exist Yet.
                </h1>
                <p class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-300">
                    We're building it.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ══════════ THE SHIFT ══════════ -->
        <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-zinc-900/30 to-black pointer-events-none"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr]">
                    <div>
                        <p
                            class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500"
                        >
                            The Shift
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-300"
                    >
                        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">
                            Something fundamental is changing.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            For decades, software executed instructions. Humans
                            decided. Humans acted. The software was a tool —
                            precise, obedient, inert.
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="text-zinc-400 text-base border-l-2 border-zinc-700 pl-5"
                        >
                            That model is ending.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            AI agents don't wait for instructions. They reason,
                            plan, and act. They book meetings, execute
                            transactions, write and deploy code, manage customer
                            relationships, and make procurement decisions —
                            autonomously, at scale, faster than any human can
                            supervise.
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-semibold text-white">
                            This is not a future scenario. It is happening now.
                            In your organization. Across every industry.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ══════════ THE PROBLEM ══════════ -->
        <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr]">
                    <div>
                        <p
                            class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500"
                        >
                            The Problem With Speed
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-300"
                    >
                        <p>
                            The agentic shift is creating economic value at a
                            pace we haven't seen since the internet. But it is
                            also creating a governance vacuum.
                        </p>
                        <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
                            <div
                                class="rounded-sm border border-zinc-600 bg-zinc-900/60 p-6"
                            >
                                <p
                                    class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2"
                                >
                                    When a human takes a business decision
                                </p>
                                <p
                                    class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed"
                                >
                                    There is a legal framework — contracts,
                                    liability, corporate law, audit trails. The
                                    accountability structure is centuries old.
                                    It is imperfect, but it exists.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="rounded-sm border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-6"
                            >
                                <p
                                    class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2"
                                >
                                    When an AI agent takes a business decision
                                </p>
                                <p
                                    class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed"
                                >
                                    There is almost nothing. The agent acts.
                                    Something happens. A log entry may or may
                                    not exist. Whether it can be trusted,
                                    verified, or produced in a regulatory
                                    inquiry is an open question for most
                                    organizations.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p>
                            Regulators have noticed. The EU AI Act, NIS-2, DORA,
                            and GDPR are not the end of the compliance wave.
                            They are the beginning.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ══════════ WHAT WE'RE BUILDING ══════════ -->
        <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-zinc-900/30 to-black pointer-events-none"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr]">
                    <div>
                        <p
                            class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500"
                        >
                            What KYDE Is Building
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-300"
                    >
                        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">
                            KYDE is building the trust infrastructure for the
                            agentic economy.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-zinc-400">
                            Not a filter. Not a firewall. Not another
                            observability dashboard.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Governance infrastructure — the layer that gives AI
                            agents real economic authority while keeping humans
                            in control of the boundaries.
                        </p>

                        <div
                            class="space-y-4 border-l-2 border-zinc-700 pl-6"
                        >
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">
                                    Near term
                                </p>
                                <p
                                    class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mt-1"
                                >
                                    A tamper-evident append-only database for
                                    every AI agent action. Evidence that cannot
                                    be altered. Records that regulators,
                                    auditors, and courts can trust.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">
                                    Longer term
                                </p>
                                <p
                                    class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mt-1"
                                >
                                    Machine-readable policies that travel with
                                    every agent. Cryptographically signed
                                    mandates. A delegation model that lets
                                    organizations give AI agents genuine
                                    authority — with verifiable, unbreakable
                                    limits.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div
                            class="rounded-sm border border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-900/40 px-8 py-6"
                        >
                            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-200">
                                Think of what corporate law did for the limited
                                liability company — it created a legal structure
                                that enabled economic actors to operate with
                                defined rights, responsibilities, and
                                accountability.
                            </p>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">
                                KYDE is building that structure for non-human
                                economic actors.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ══════════ WHY NOW ══════════ -->
        <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr]">
                    <div>
                        <p
                            class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500"
                        >
                            Why Now
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <p class="text-lg text-zinc-300 mb-10">
                            Three forces are converging.
                        </p>
                        <div class="space-y-6">
                            {
                                [
                                    {
                                        n: "01",
                                        title: "Regulatory enforcement is real.",
                                        body: "EU AI Act High-Risk enforcement begins August 2, 2026. NIS-2 is already in force. DORA is in force. The compliance deadlines are not hypothetical.",
                                        color: "amber",
                                    },
                                    {
                                        n: "02",
                                        title: "Agent deployment is accelerating.",
                                        body: "Every major enterprise is running AI agents today — often without knowing exactly what those agents are doing, why, or whether the record of their actions can be trusted.",
                                        color: "blue",
                                    },
                                    {
                                        n: "03",
                                        title: "The window to define the infrastructure layer is open.",
                                        body: "Trust infrastructure, like all infrastructure, is built once and depended on for decades. The organization that defines the governance standard for AI agents becomes the foundation everything else is built on.",
                                        color: "cyan",
                                    },
                                ].map(({ n, title, body, color }) => (
                                    <div
                                        class={`flex gap-6 rounded-sm border bg-zinc-900/40 p-8 ${"border-zinc-700"}`}
                                    >
                                        <span
                                            class={`font-mono text-3xl font-bold shrink-0 ${"text-zinc-700"}`}
                                        >
                                            {n}
                                        </span>
                                        <div>
                                            <p class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2">
                                                {title}
                                            </p>
                                            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
                                                {body}
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                ))
                            }
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ══════════ CTA ══════════ -->
        <section class="py-24 md:py-32">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
                <div
                    class="rounded-sm border border-zinc-700 p-12 md:p-16"
                >
                    <div class="max-w-2xl">
                        <h2
                            class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white"
                        >
                            Want to learn more or get involved?
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-300">
                            We're early. If you're building in regulated
                            industries, we want to talk.
                        </p>
                        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                            <button
                                onclick="openModal()"
                                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-black hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-all"
                            >
                                Book a Demo →
                            </button>
                            <a
                                href="mailto:hello@kyde.com"
                                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-zinc-700 px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200 hover:border-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-all"
                            >
                                hello@kyde.com
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Base>
